init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You say to him, "I wish I was you."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I was you in your last life, and I'll be you in your next life."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look ahead and see a white beam of light.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What did you do in your life to become so miserable?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I was a prostitute, and I contracted AIDS," she replies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I was raped on a daily basis, and I died of drug overdose at the age of 41."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I watched that life in real-time, too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: ," the two versions of yourself say in unison.
